reviewText: Video and sound are very good. It's silly, hilarious, zany slapstick comedy.  A must for any Abbott and Costello fan.  There are four 30 minute shows.  #1 "Little Old Lady"; the boys try to help evicted mrs. Gillicuddy.  #2 "Bank Holdup"; the boys become unwitting accomplices in a holdup.  #3"Dentist Office"; some hilarious slapstick in a dentist office.  #4"Fencing Master"; lou challanges the fencing ace upstairs to a duel.
